data.description: Brand new, energy-efficient home available by Aug 2023! Enjoy a large laundry room and primary walk-in closet in the Leslie. Entertain friends and family in your spacious great room and kitchen complete with a kitchen island. Models are now open at Bella Vista Farms - Estate Series in San Tan Valley. Your family will love spending time outside at the community pool, playgrounds, walking trails and sports fields. Each energy-efficient home also comes standard with features that go beyond helping you save on utility bills—they allow your whole family to live better and breathe easier too.*  Each of our homes is built with innovative, energy-efficient features designed to help you enjoy more savings, better health, real comfort and peace of mind.
